OL,3,CTributes to 'legendary' defence
OL,4,Cbarrister Courtenay Griffiths KC
OL,6,FThe British legal world has paid
OL,7,Ftribute to "legendary" defence
OL,8,Fbarrister Courtenay Griffiths KC, who
OL,9,Fhas died at the age of 69.
OL,11,FJamaica-born Dr Griffiths was among
OL,12,Fthe first black lawyers to be awarded
OL,13,Fthe then-Queen's Counsel status and
OL,14,Frose to become a most prominent and
OL,15,Fformidable force at the criminal bar.
OL,17,FHe defended in many high-profile
OL,18,Fcriminal trials after he was called to
OL,19,Fthe bar in July 1980 and awarded silk
OL,20,Fin 1998.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@VO]
