OL,3,CTributes to 'legendary' defence
OL,4,Cbarrister Courtenay Griffiths KC
OL,6,FNotable cases included the Pc Keith
OL,7,FBlakelock murder trial, the Brighton
OL,8,Fbombing and the Damilola Taylor murder
OL,9,Ftrial.
OL,11,FIn 2007 he represented former Liberia
OL,12,Fpresident Charles Taylor in his war
OL,13,Fcrimes trial in The Hague and also sat
OL,14,Fas a part-time judge.
OL,16,FBarrister Laurie-Anne Power KC, of 25
OL,17,FBedford Row, said: "He was the single
OL,18,Fmost influential figure in my legal
OL,19,Fcareer.
OL,26,@yD@TOU
