OL,3,CTributes to 'legendary' defence
OL,4,Cbarrister Courtenay Griffiths KC
OL,6,F"He epitomised brilliance, intellect
OL,7,Fand fearlessness in equal measure.
OL,9,F"He considered it his duty to open
OL,10,Fdoors and provide opportunities to
OL,11,Fthose who might not otherwise have
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,F"He was unapologetic about changing
OL,15,Fthe landscape of the bar.
OL,17,F"As an advocate, there was simply no-
OL,18,Fone better.
OL,20,F"He commanded the attention of anyone
OL,21,Fand everyone in the courtroom.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU|D@AOU
