OL,3,CTributes to 'legendary' defence
OL,4,Cbarrister Courtenay Griffiths KC
OL,6,F"He had it all in abundance.
OL,8,F"But behind the advocate was a gentle,
OL,9,Fkind, and selfless man who loved the
OL,10,Flaw."
OL,12,FMs Power said she first met Dr
OL,13,FGriffiths at a law fair in 1998 and he
OL,14,Fimmediately asked her if she was
OL,15,FJamaican after sharing stories of
OL,16,Ftheir mutual love for the island.
OL,18,FShe added: "He was my only mentor, in
OL,19,Fthe true sense of the word.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@AOUrD@EO]zD@LOU
