OL,3,CTributes to 'legendary' defence
OL,4,Cbarrister Courtenay Griffiths KC
OL,6,F"He hounded me into applying for silk
OL,7,Fand did not stop until I got it.
OL,9,F"He was a friend first and made me
OL,10,Fbelieve that I could achieve anything
OL,11,Fwithin the profession."
OL,13,FITV News senior correspondent Ronke
OL,14,FPhillips said: "To watch Courtenay
OL,15,FGriffiths in action at the Old Bailey
OL,16,Fwas compelling.
OL,18,F"He was a skilled advocate. Sharp,
OL,19,Fclever and when needed, witty.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUsD@WO]vD@POUzD@AOU
