OL,3,CTributes to 'legendary' defence
OL,4,Cbarrister Courtenay Griffiths KC
OL,6,FWriting on X, Jacqueline McKenzie,
OL,7,Fsolicitor and partner at law firm
OL,8,FLeigh Day, said: "Through his practice
OL,9,Fat Garden Court and 25 Bedford Row
OL,10,FChambers, he acted in major criminal
OL,11,Fand human rights cases, in the UK and
OL,12,Foverseas, and left an indelible mark
OL,13,Fof greatness on our profession, and on
OL,14,Fthe world."
OL,16,FBarrister Amina Graham, from 2 Hare
OL,17,FCourt Chambers, wrote on LinkedIn: "He
OL,18,Fdemonstrated the importance of
OL,19,Frepresentation for me in my pursuit of
OL,20,Fa career at the Bar.
OL,26,@pD@ROUvD@KO]yD@dOU
