OL,3,CTributes to 'legendary' defence
OL,4,Cbarrister Courtenay Griffiths KC
OL,6,F"I worked with him during my time at
OL,7,Fthe Special Court for Sierra Leona
OL,8,Fwhere he represented Charles Taylor
OL,9,F... a formidable advocate and an
OL,10,Finspiration to so many."
OL,12,FDr Griffiths was a multi-award-winning
OL,13,Fbarrister who spent the majority of
OL,14,Fhis career between Garden Court
OL,15,FChambers and 25 Bedford Row.
OL,17,FIn 2020, Dr Griffiths was handed an
OL,18,Foutstanding achievement award at the
OL,19,FLegal 500 Awards and was given a
OL,20,Flifetime achievement award at the UK
OL,21,FDiversity Legal Awards in 2018.
